---

<Layout>
  <header class="px-2.5 py-32 flex-col justify-center items-center gap-8 flex">
    <div class="inline-flex flex-col justify-start items-center gap-4">
      <h1 class="relative overflow-hidden inline-block align-bottom font-mono text-8xl text-white gradient">Build Something Cool</h1>
      <span class="text-center text-white text-2xl font-black">at</span>
      <h1
        class="flex w-full text-center justify-center items-center uppercase font-black md:text-6xl text-4xl dark:text-white text-black"
      >
        Hamp
        <svg
          xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
          viewBox="0 0 1080 1080"
          class="md:h-12 h-8"
          aria-label="HampHack Lightning Bolt"
        >
          <defs>
            <style>
              .c {
                fill: #61ff61;
              }
            </style>
          </defs>
          <g id="a">
            <path
              class="c"
              d="M890.57,404.25h-278.6c-15.11,0-27.36-12.25-27.36-27.36V27.41c0-27.84-36.72-37.89-50.91-13.95L165.89,634.44c-10.8,18.24,2.34,41.31,23.54,41.31H468.03c15.11,0,27.36,12.25,27.36,27.36v349.48c0,27.84,36.72,37.89,50.91,13.95L914.11,445.56c10.8-18.24-2.34-41.31-23.54-41.31Z"
            >
            </path>
          </g>
          <g id="b"></g>
        </svg>
        Hack
      </h1>
    </div>

    <a
      href="https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSf2ozqZ9vJpGBHVP7DfQ80xmVKKqDc4LE-ui5s3DGVOlOYlLA/viewform"
      target="_blank"
      rel="noopener noreferrer"
      class="px-6 py-2 bg-green-500 rounded-xl justify-center items-center gap-2.5 inline-flex"
    >
      <div class="text-black text-2xl font-normal font-mono">Register Now</div>
    </a>

    <div class="flex-col justify-center items-center gap-3 inline-flex">
      <div class="text-center text-white text-xl font-black">
        March 29th - March 31st
      </div>
      <div class="text-center text-white text-xl font-black">
        R.W. Kern Center, Hampshire College
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="flex-col justify-end items-center gap-2.5 inline-flex mt-36">
      <div class="flex-col justify-center items-center gap-2 flex">
        <div class="text-white text-2xl font-normal font-mono">Read More</div>
        <ArrowDownIcon className="text-white h-6 w-6 animate-bounce" />
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="px-2.5 py-16 flex-col justify-start items-center gap-12 inline-flex">
      <div class="flex-col justify-start items-center gap-3 flex">
          <span class="text-center text-white text-2xl font-black">HampHack is</span>
          <h1 class="text-white text-7xl font-normal font-mono">An Interdisciplinary Creative Event</h1>
      </div>
      <div class="self-stretch p-2.5 justify-center items-start gap-2.5 inline-flex">
          <div class="p-10 bg-neutral-900 flex-col justify-start items-center gap-2.5 inline-flex">
              <Twemoji className="w-32 h-32" emoji="🤝" />
              <div class="text-center text-white text-4xl font-normal font-mono">Form a Team</div>
              <div class="text-center text-white text-lg font-bold">Create one with friends<br/>or join one with strangers!</div>
          </div>
          <div class="p-10 bg-neutral-900 flex-col justify-start items-center gap-2.5 inline-flex">
              <Twemoji className="w-32 h-32" emoji="🤔" />
              <div class="text-center text-white text-4xl font-normal font-mono">Propose Your Idea</div>
              <div class="text-center text-white text-lg font-bold">Think of something you want to work on,<br/>optionally from one of our themes.</div>
          </div>
          <div class="p-10 bg-neutral-900 flex-col justify-start items-center gap-2.5 inline-flex">
              <Twemoji className="w-32 h-32" emoji="🏗️" />
              <div class="text-center text-white text-4xl font-normal font-mono">Make the Thing</div>
              <div class="text-center text-white text-lg font-bold">Now build it!<br/>You have 24 hours.</div>
          </div>
      </div>
      <div class="flex-col justify-start items-center gap-3 flex">
          <div class="text-center text-white text-2xl font-black">HampHack is</div>
          <div class="text-white text-7xl font-normal font-mono">For everyone</div>
      </div>
      <div class="self-stretch p-2.5 justify-center items-start gap-2.5 inline-flex">
          <div class="px-10 py-5 bg-neutral-900 flex-col justify-start items-center gap-2.5 inline-flex">
              <div class="text-center text-white text-4xl font-normal font-mono">Beginner?</div>
              <div class="text-center text-white text-lg font-bold">Awesome!! Come learn<br/>something new.</div>
          </div>
          <div class="px-10 py-5 bg-neutral-900 flex-col justify-start items-center gap-2.5 inline-flex">
              <div class="text-center text-white text-4xl font-normal font-mono">Familiar?</div>
              <div class="text-center text-white text-lg font-bold">Great! Lets expand your<br/>horizons.</div>
          </div>
          <div class="px-10 py-5 bg-neutral-900 flex-col justify-start items-center gap-2.5 inline-flex">
              <div class="text-center text-white text-4xl font-normal font-mono">Experienced?</div>
              <div class="text-center text-white text-lg font-bold">Amazing! Show off your<br/>talent, or help others.</div>
          </div>
      </div>
      <div class="flex-col justify-start items-center gap-3 flex">
          <div class="text-white text-7xl font-normal font-mono">FAQ</div>
      </div>
      <div class="self-stretch h-[1150px] px-32 py-2.5 flex-col justify-start items-center gap-4 flex">
          <div class="self-stretch h-[194px] px-10 py-5 bg-neutral-900 flex-col justify-center items-center gap-2.5 flex">
              <div class="self-stretch text-center text-white text-4xl font-normal font-mono">I see &quot;Hack&quot; in the name. Is this about computers?</div>
              <div class="text-center text-white text-xl font-bold">Nope! We use the word &quot;Hack&quot; loosely, attributed with &quot;Hackathon&quot;.<br/>This is an event to show off your talents to simply make something cool!</div>
          </div>
          <div class="self-stretch h-[242px] px-10 py-5 bg-neutral-900 flex-col justify-center items-center gap-2.5 flex">
              <div class="self-stretch text-center text-white text-4xl font-normal font-mono">I don&apos;t know how to code. Is this event right for me?</div>
              <div class="text-center text-white text-xl font-bold">Absolutely! You can learn some basics,<br/>or you can bring your unique talents to a team!<br/>We encourage beginners to come.</div>
          </div>
          <div class="self-stretch h-[194px] px-10 py-5 bg-neutral-900 flex-col justify-center items-center gap-2.5 flex">
              <div class="self-stretch text-center text-white text-4xl font-normal font-mono">Will there be food?</div>
              <div class="text-center text-white text-xl font-bold">Yup! We&apos;ll be providing catered food. If you have an allergy,<br/>please let us know in your registration!</div>
          </div>
          <div class="self-stretch h-[290px] px-10 py-5 bg-neutral-900 flex-col justify-center items-center gap-2.5 flex">
              <div class="self-stretch text-center text-white text-4xl font-normal font-mono">I have an accessibility need, will I be okay?</div>
              <div class="text-center text-white text-xl font-bold">We will try our best to accommodate to your needs. The event is taking place<br/>at the R.W. Kern Center at Hampshire College, which is an ADA-compliant<br/>building. Please let us know what accommodations you may need ahead of time<br/>in your registration.</div>
          </div>
          <div class="self-stretch h-[146px] px-10 py-5 bg-neutral-900 flex-col justify-center items-center gap-2.5 flex">
              <div class="self-stretch text-center text-white text-4xl font-normal font-mono">Are there any restrictions on who can participate?</div>
              <div class="text-center text-white text-xl font-bold">You must be over 18. Nothing personal, just bureaucracy.</div>
          </div>
      </div>
  </div>
  </header>
</Layout>
